{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not that it moved closer, it's just that it's easier to get there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's-- and it's in the same general area, I would say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's further north-- northeast of where we live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1927, and my sister was born in 1928.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Edith.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the same name she had in German, Edith.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she always kept the same name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, I was born in 1932, and my name, as I said originally, was Fritz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say traditional household.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were, traditionally, religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're not Orthodox like the Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we used-- I think it was kosher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It probably was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then, later on, you couldn't keep kosher because the-- the-- it was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The ritual slaughter was forbidden in Germany after Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I-- I don't think that-- by the time I remember well, I don't think it was kosher.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Couldn't have been because it wasn't-- you could no longer buy kosher meat or anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vaguely Passover.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember-- I also remember, vaguely, going to the synagogue, but I don't remember that well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we had-- we had in the town, an orphanage where I used to go to a lot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This orphanage, really, was a Jewish orphanage, which was run-- it was for the whole Rhineland, for the whole area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was run by Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Leopold Rothschild, who was a well-known educator and very respected man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And even though I wasn't-- I was like a half an orphan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's not-- that's not the reason I went there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The reason was, it was a safe place to go to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a big house with-- with fence-- with a fence around it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It had a back to play.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could go and play there without being bothered by the-- by other kids.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember that in-- I used to go with my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Behind the house there was a park.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we used to-- he used to take me for a walk there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the older kids used to throw stones at us and call us dirty Jew, and-- and-- and the adults used to turn the other way or help them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember playing with other kids, and-- and one of the things I remember, I guess, because it was scary-- one of the things they-- they started to-- to do is dig trenches.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess, this was under the influence of the adults.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they were preparing for war-- dig trenches and then, sit in them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember I played with them, and-- and I sat in the trench, and they started to throw the sand on me from-- you know, from outside till one of the mothers from the other kids came and pulled me out.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, in those days it had, maybe, 20,000 inhabitants, but it was a very strong Jewish community-- small, but strong, very nice synagogue.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And like I said, it was one of the reasons it was so well-- so strong-- was because of the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think that helped to sort of make it a strong community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, this Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rothschild was Orthodox-- you know, modern Orthodox, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was a very strong individual and had a lot of influence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't even remember whether there was a rabbi or not in-- in the community.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know there was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember if there was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I know that a lot of things he did, and he was, more or less, the leader of the community in many ways.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as I could remember, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, I couldn't go out and play.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I played with other kids, but it was-- after a while, it became dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, when the time came to go to school-- to kindergarten-- go to school, we couldn't anymore because Jewish kids could not go to the same school as-- as other kids.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had established a Jewish school, which I went to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I-- I guess the community must have been big enough to support-- it was a small school, but it-- it-- it supported a school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know whether-- I'm sure they got a few Jewish families in little villages in the area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They probably came there, too, I imagine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember the name of the teacher, even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, there was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He lived-- he was the gentleman who lived-- who rented a room from my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he taught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was the teacher there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think there's only one teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember anybody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Might have been teacher's aids, but I don't-- don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
